><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>，宣傳片將於星期六晚上10時半在《翡翠台》首播，警方Facebook亦將於當晚11時上載片段。"},{"pid":"66ad018168f4343b7e6272f310594498f1a01061","tid":2374764,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428f2afb226590dde50ae49f73229fba1b870c92","tid":2374764,"uid":34789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"新宣傳片《守城》講述恐怖份子在本港多個地點脅持人質，警方出動多個部隊解決事件，期間出動約600名警員，涉及15個警方單位<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味初選大圍捕都過千警力啦<br />\n呢套得600咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a924e60dbe582da665d56d1b3157fea9ac306e","tid":2374764,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:18:53.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n啲錢用黎比你班狗打飛機？"},{"pid":"cd05c40267d34029b06e7c1695529abc34e284c6","tid":2374764,"uid":127067,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:39:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/M75YHTDPJRERZO3US7CWGRWEXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FM75YHTDPJRERZO3US7CWGRWEXM%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcLXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=aa213816\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FM75YHTDPJRERZO3US7CWGRWEXM%2F&h=2f6ff380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/M75YHTDPJRERZO3US7CWGRWEXM/</a><br />\n<br />\n哦 靠犯法擾民拍出嚟個套？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edfbf53eabd883764ebbf6d003fd